# Architecture Karibloom — Next.js 15 App Router

> Complète — ne remplace pas — `kb-supabase.mdc`, `kb-auth.mdc`, `kb-forms.mdc`, `kb-stripe.mdc`.
> Stack : Next.js 15.2.4 (App Router) · React 19 · TypeScript strict · Supabase 2.45 · Stripe 14.25 · Chakra UI 3 + HeroUI + Radix Themes + Tailwind 3.4.

